261
00:32:20,618 --> 00:32:23,610
To je znak Kfar Riata

262
00:32:24,656 --> 00:32:27,557
To je zatvor na jugu.

263
00:32:31,629 --> 00:32:33,756
Vi niste culi za Kfar Riat?

264
00:32:33,898 --> 00:32:35,097
- Ne.

265
00:32:35,098 --> 00:32:38,499
- Vi definitivno niste odavde.

266
00:32:39,770 --> 00:32:42,603
Vi ne znate za Jug.

267
00:33:15,470 --> 00:33:17,597
Ako medjunarodna zajednica

268
00:33:18,873 --> 00:33:21,501
sada ne intervenise,

269
00:33:22,978 --> 00:33:24,502
izbeglice

270
00:33:26,046 --> 00:33:30,540
u pretrpanim logorima na granici.....

271
00:33:33,853 --> 00:33:35,343
- Stigla je.

272
00:33:35,488 --> 00:33:36,688
- OK.

273
00:33:36,723 --> 00:33:39,487
Mi,studenti,se protivimo Nacionalistickoj partiji

274
00:33:39,626 --> 00:33:41,992
koja pokusava da protera izbeglice preko granice.

275
00:33:42,161 --> 00:33:43,492
- Nacionalisticka stranka podrzava

276
00:33:43,663 --> 00:33:45,187
milicije hriscanske desnice,

277
00:33:45,331 --> 00:33:47,231
koje otvoreno prete izbeglicama.

278
00:33:47,367 --> 00:33:49,358
-Na Jugu,izbeglice su sada naoruzane.

279
00:33:49,502 --> 00:33:51,299
I... oni podrzavaju

280
00:33:51,404 --> 00:33:55,703
mnogobrojno muslimansko stanovnistvo u zemlji.

281
00:33:55,841 --> 00:33:59,038
- Ali ti... ali ti si hriscanka.

282
00:33:59,177 --> 00:34:01,668
- Ja, ja sam za mir.

283
00:34:01,813 --> 00:34:04,179
Religija nema nikakve veze sa tim.

284
00:34:13,824 --> 00:34:15,024
- Nawal!

285
00:34:15,526 --> 00:34:18,016
Ukljucite radio!
Upravo su zatvorili univerzitet!

286
00:34:18,194 --> 00:34:20,856
Nacionalisti su zatvorili Univerzitet!

287
00:34:36,279 --> 00:34:38,042
- Nawal, vrati se.

288
00:34:38,848 --> 00:34:40,509
Ostani ovde.

289
00:34:43,619 --> 00:34:46,110
Ujace Charbel,
Nacionalisti zatvaraju univerzitet!

290
00:34:46,388 --> 00:34:50,084
Bice sukoba.

291
00:34:50,258 --> 00:34:52,419
Ostani ovde samnom.

292
00:35:11,144 --> 00:35:12,344
Bilo je pucnjave napolju...

293
00:35:15,048 --> 00:35:16,248
Postavite sto,devojke!

294
00:35:16,383 --> 00:35:18,248
Mama, napadaju univerzitet!

295
00:35:18,385 --> 00:35:21,115
- To nije razlog da se ne jede!

296
00:35:29,095 --> 00:35:30,585
- Aioua?

297
00:36:00,792 --> 00:36:04,090
Jutros su napadnuta hriscanska sela na jugu.

298
00:36:04,261 --> 00:36:06,354
- Boze zastiti nas!

299
00:36:06,530 --> 00:36:08,520
-Zbog toga su oni zatvorili univerzitet.

300
00:36:08,698 --> 00:36:12,031
Veoma brzo,i ovde ce eksplodirati.

301
00:36:13,636 --> 00:36:18,505
Mi idemo na planinu dok se ne smiri.

302
00:36:19,475 --> 00:36:20,965
- Kada krecemo?

303
00:36:21,644 --> 00:36:22,844
-Krecemo sutra.

304
00:36:22,879 --> 00:36:25,643
Ostatak porodice je vec tamo.

305
00:36:25,815 --> 00:36:27,304
- A skola?

306
00:36:28,450 --> 00:36:30,816
- U svakom slucaju,zatvorice skole.

307
00:36:31,319 --> 00:36:33,287
Bog zna kolko dugo.

308
00:36:33,822 --> 00:36:35,050
- A novine?

309
00:36:35,891 --> 00:36:37,381
-Ne boj se.

310
00:36:37,559 --> 00:36:40,960
Novine mogu da prezive bez tebe neko vreme.

311
00:36:41,797 --> 00:36:44,823
-Ali ideje opstaju ako ima ko da ih brani!

312
00:36:45,000 --> 00:36:46,796
- Tacno, Rafqa.

313
00:36:47,868 --> 00:36:49,460
Upravo tako.

314
00:37:01,014 --> 00:37:03,676
-Postoje samo dva sirotista u regionu.

315
00:37:03,817 --> 00:37:05,682
Uskoro cu ti se pridruziti.

316
00:37:05,852 --> 00:37:08,013
-Neces samnom sada!

317
00:37:09,889 --> 00:37:12,187
Obecala si baki da ces zavrsiti studije.

318
00:37:12,358 --> 00:37:13,882
- Cula si svog oca.

319
00:37:14,027 --> 00:37:17,053
Da ce eksplodirati sirom zemlje ako oni napadnu univerzitet.

320
00:37:18,064 --> 00:37:19,530
Studiranje je zavrseno.

321
00:37:24,236 --> 00:37:25,862
Mislim na njega svaki dan.

322
00:37:26,037 --> 00:37:27,698
To je moje dete.

323
00:37:28,940 --> 00:37:30,669
Hocu da ga nadjem zivog.

324
00:37:51,795 --> 00:37:54,263
