325
00:37:54,431 --> 00:37:56,695
-Pozuri, Nawal.

326
00:39:56,044 --> 00:39:57,841
- Vase ime?
- Nawal.

327
00:39:58,013 --> 00:40:00,345
- Nawal kako?
- Nawal Marwan.

328
00:40:01,182 --> 00:40:02,382
- Gde idete?

329
00:40:02,750 --> 00:40:03,883
- Na jug.

330
00:40:03,884 --> 00:40:05,084
-Zasto?

331
00:40:05,653 --> 00:40:07,382
-Da bi se pridruzila suprugu.

332
00:42:29,387 --> 00:42:30,820
Wahabe.

333
00:42:57,514 --> 00:42:59,914
