339
00:44:49,018 --> 00:44:51,350
-Treba da pitate one koji su bili tu.

340
00:44:51,520 --> 00:44:56,924
Mestani muslimani su pobegli u kamp Deressa.

341
00:44:57,426 --> 00:45:00,020
